Package: kwb.tenders
Title: R Package for Automated Monitoring of German Public Procurement
    Portals (Vergabeportale) for KWB-Relevant Tenders
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Michael", "Rustler", , "michael.rustler@kompetenz-wasser.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0647-7726")),
    person("Kompetenzzentrum Wasser Berlin gGmbH (KWB)", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Logs into public procurement portals (starting with
    Vergabemarktplatz Brandenburg), scrapes published tenders, scores them
    for relevance to KWB research topics (e.g. groundwater) and renders an
    overview report.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/KWB-R/kwb.tenders
BugReports: https://github.com/KWB-R/kwb.tenders/issues
